ActCanada Wildlife Act
SubjectEdéhzhíe National Wildlife Area in the N.W.T ** Acquisition of lands **
PrecisOrder Auhorizing the Minister of the Environment to acquire lands to be added subsequently to the EDÉHZHÍE NATIONAL WILDLIFE AREA in the Northwest Territories for the purpose of research, conservation and interpretation in respect of migratory birds, and to support the Department of the Environment's commitment to preserve Canada's wildlife and preserve the country's natural heritage.
